                  <persName role="owner" corresp="PRS0000">Wäldä Mikaʾel is mentioned in the supplication formulas throughout the Ms., sometimes together with his wife Wälättä Gäbrǝʾel (e.g., fol. 6va), his father Täsfa Maryam (e.g., fol. 7ra), his mother Wälättä ʾAnanya (e.g., fol. 7ra) and other relatives.&#xD;
